short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Manage your friends list, track engagement and locate inactive profiles to unfriend on your Facebook™ page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
FriendFilter gives you an easy way to manage your friends list, track engagement and locate inactive profiles to unfriend on your Facebook™ page.
